      "difficulty": "中等",
      "content": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6\">\n        <span class=\"tag-ta-render px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">TA渲染专栏</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">Thu, 26 Fe</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">•</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">5分钟阅读</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">•</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">初级特效师、技术美术</span>\n    </div>\n    <h1>UE5 Niagara 粘液特效制作技巧：新手入门指南</h1>\n    <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6\">Niagara 是虚幻引擎5的新一代粒子系统，本教程详细讲解如何使用 Niagara 制作逼真的粘液、史莱姆类特效。涵盖了材质制作、粒子行为设置、物理属性调整等核心技术点，适合 Niagara 初学者系统学习。</p>\n    <div class=\"source-box\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n            <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-neon-amber\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1\"></path>\n            </svg>\n            <span class=\"text-neon-amber font-medium\">原文链接</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\">\n            <div>• <a href=\"https://realtimevfx.com/t/new-to-niagra-ue5-how-would-i-go-about-recreating-this-slash-effect/30490\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-neon-blue hover:underline\">Realtime VFX - 查看完整原文</a></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tech-analysis-box\" style=\"border-color: #00ff8840;\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">\n            <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"color: #00ff88\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z\"></path>\n            </svg>\n            <span class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"color: #00ff88\">🔬 深度技术分析</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mb-0 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">粘液类特效的核心挑战在于模拟半透明的、有体积感的流体外观。在 Niagara 中，这类效果通常结合 GPU Sprite 粒子与自定义材质实现。技术要点包括：使用 Subsurface Scattering（次表面散射）模拟光线穿透粘液的效果，通过 World Position Offset 添加波动动画，利用 Niagara 的 Dynamic Parameter 传递粒子属性到材质。对于性能优化，可以使用 Flipbook 动画替代实时模拟，在保持视觉质量的同时大幅降低计算开销。这种效果广泛应用于 RPG 游戏中的史莱姆怪物、科幻题材的能量粘液等场景。</p>\n    </div>\n    <h2>🎯 核心技术点</h2>\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\">\n        <div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #00ff88\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #00ff88\">Niagara粒子系统</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #00ff88\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #00ff88\">Subsurface Scattering</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #00ff88\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #00ff88\">Flipbook纹理</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #00ff88\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #00ff88\">材质Shader</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div>\n    </div>\n    <h2>💡 实用价值与应用场景</h2>\n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-dark-700/50 to-dark-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-0\">掌握 Niagara 制作流体类特效的核心方法，可应用于游戏中的怪物特效、环境互动效果等</p>\n    </div>\n    <h2>🏷️ 技术标签</h2>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"tag-ta-render px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">Niagara粒子系统</span><span class=\"tag-ta-render px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">Subsurface Scattering</span><span class=\"tag-ta-render px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">Flipbook纹理</span><span class=\"tag-ta-render px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">材质Shader</span></div>\n    <h2>📚 相关技术主题</h2>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">Niagara特效</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">流体模拟</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">游戏特效</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">材质制作</span></div>\n    <h2>👥 适合人群与难度</h2>\n    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\">\n        <li><strong>目标读者:</strong> 初级特效师、技术美术</li>\n        <li><strong>实现难度:</strong> 中等</li>\n        <li><strong>技术领域:</strong> TA渲染专栏</li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #00ff88\">\n        <p class=\"mb-0 text-gray-400\">\n            <strong style=\"color: #00ff88\">💡 提示:</strong> \n            本文为高质量中文技术分析，由AI基于原文深度整理。如需查看完整原文，请点击上方链接。\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</div>",
